_refine.details                                  
;Bulk solvent terms included in Fob file created with standard X-PLOR script.
Only Leu_A9 to Thr_A17 are included for the A-chain.
Residues prior and after these residues are not visible (disordered).
Residues after Glu B245 are not visible (disordered).
                                                     
Residues simultaneously refined in two or more conformations are: 
Ile_B17, Met_B47, Met_B81, Glu_B84, Glu_B86, Arg_B116, Leu_B123, Thr_B139,
Arg_B166, Gln_B192, Met_B207, Lys_B223, Ser_B232, Leu_B235,
part of citrate_3

No energy terms between citrate 1 and 2 are included because they appear
to be hydrogen-bonded to one another via an unusually short hydrogen bond
between carboxylate groups.

Disordered waters are: 
HOH33 which is close to HOH36; 
HOH104 which is close to HOH107
HOH155 which is close to conformation 1 of Glu_B84
HOH283 which is close to HOH285;
HOH373 which is close to HOH374;
HOH715 which is close to HOH720 which is close to HOH721
;
